cs.SE, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.PL, cs.DC 

The paper discusses the challenges of quality assurance in self-adaptive systems, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SY) categories. The paper also proposes a paradigm for adaptive testing, which involves the use of test cases and constraints that evolve in parallel to the development of the system-under-test, which relates to artificial intelligence (cs.AI), programming languages (cs.PL), and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
